                <h1>Change Background Color in PowerPoint: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To change the background color in PowerPoint, open your presentation and select the slide you want to modify. Go to the "Design" tab and click on "Format Background." Choose "Solid Fill" for a single color or "Gradient Fill" for a blend. Select your desired color and apply it to all slides or just the current one.</p>
